'''V1-CH''' was a [[Droid/Legends|droid]] belonging to [[TriNebulon News/Legends|TriNebulon News]] reporter [[Andor Javin]]. V1-CH helped Javin uncover a possible link between [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggler]] [[Platt Okeefe/Legends|Platt Okeefe]], and rogue newsnet operator [[Cynabar]].

